            . I live with my father, Thomas Walker, a <rs id="t18260914-219-viclabel1256" type="occupation">pawnbroker</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260914-219-victim1250 t18260914-219-viclabel1256"></join>. The prisoner came to our shop on the 24th of July; I saw him at the door, handling some handkerchiefs, and in a minute or two he pulled them down and walked away; I seized him round the corner - he said he was starving.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260914-219-person1252">
                  EDWARD 
                  WILLIAM WOOD
               <interp inst="t18260914-219-person1252" type="surname" value="WILLIAM WOOD"></interp>
