                     <interp inst="t18260914-219-person1252" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was coming down Tabernacle-row, and saw a man coming out of Mr. Walker's shop, drawing these handkerchiefs under his arm.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was up in town without a bit of bread for two days, and was tempted by hunger to take them.</p>
               <p>
